HEADWORD: Biostatics
<hw>Bi`o*stat"ics</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>bi`os</grk> life + <ets><?/</ets>. See <er>Statics</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>The physical phenomena of organized bodies, in
opposition to their organic or vital phenomena.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Biostatistics</ent>⟦br⟧
